FT  25 MAR 94 / Operators to pay landfill charges
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The cost of monitoring and inspecting licensed landfill rubbish dumps will
be transfered from the taxpayer to waste management companies from May, Mr
Robert Atkins, environment minister, announced yesterday.
The new rules are part of the government's much-postponed waste management
licensing regulation, which comes into force on May 1. Mr Atkins said the
change was 'an important extension of the 'polluter pays' principle'.
