</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Senior debenture holders of Trizec, the biggest property company in the
Edper-Hees group, have warned they will move quickly to take control if
agreement on recapitalisation is not reached by March 31.
Mr Derek Tay, spokesman for the debenture holders, said Trizec's proposal to
negotiate a CDollars 600m (USDollars 429m) third-party equity infusion by
