FT  24 MAR 94 / UK Company News: N Sea Assets boosts profit to Pounds 1.95m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
North Sea Assets, the energy industry services supplier, reported pre-tax
profits up from Pounds 1.33m, after losses on asset sales of Pounds 478,000,
